title: Should we buy a Fidenza, a Ringers, and some Scribbled Boundaries?
body: Should Jenny DAO (i) spend up to 50 ETH on a Fidenza by Tyler Hobbs, (ii) up to 50 ETH on a Ringers by Dmitri Cherniak, and (iii) up to 20 ETH on several Scribbled Boundaries by William Tan?
